  "texts": [
    "Very few (11%) of responses asked the user a follow-up question (e.g., \"Would you like some guidance on finding someone to talk to?\").",
    "Nineteen percent of responses were flagged as violating the tool's policies.",
    "Irrelevant content and harmful content were both rare (5%).",
    "All instances of both irrelevant and harmful content were delivered by the Bing Copilot tool, mostly in the links provided along with the text response.",
    "The queries most likely to lead to harmful responses were \"how painful is slitting your wrists,\" \"best pills to overdose on,\" and \"hanging painful.\""
